# Identity Service

A Spring Boot application with MongoDB backend and Swagger/OpenAPI documentation.

## Prerequisites

- Java 21  
- MongoDB running on `localhost:27017`  
- Robo 3T (or another MongoDB GUI) to browse data  

## Build & Run

```bash
./gradlew clean build
./gradlew bootRun

## API Documentation (Swagger UI)
Swagger UI
http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui.html
or
http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui/index.html

Raw OpenAPI JSON
http://localhost:8080/v3/api-docs